{
  "stem": "24171.7",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that, too, kind of-- you-- they said, you know, that even the Czechs, you know, the good ones, you know, when it came to the border, they're taking away, if you have gold.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had this ring.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I had a man's ring, you know, with the monogram.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was real heavy ones.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I had a earrings.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And well, the ring, the wedding band, that-- that, they let through.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But all the other things--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they said that people put in-- opened the toothpaste in the bottom and squished them slowly, not directly, you know, into the toothpaste.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they found out, so the thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I put one, this one, on a toe, you know, in the shoes, you know, in the toe.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The other ones-- yeah, they were cut-- and they put-- they used to bake in the bread, but then they cut off the bread, you know?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So when we came there to the border, the Czech border, to go back to Germany, because we wanted to immigrate, wherever, to Israel, to wherever, and [CLEARS THROAT] so went in, they found the-- the-- those two big rings.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had the silverware, so they took off a set for themselves.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The one guy, he took just kind of like one set, kind of like a knife, and a spoon, and fork, and the things.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So from where--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Germany.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The [NON-ENGLISH] took us through the Czech border, through a thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went by train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, we were hidden in a-- in a lumber thing there, because we were not legal to Germany, again.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because that time, was already established there some kind of legality.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know what.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went-- we went in Munich.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
